---

<div class="w-full lg:w-[340px] lg:flex-shrink-0 p-6 lg:p-8 lg:sticky lg:top-0 lg:h-screen lg:overflow-y-auto">
  <div class="lg:pt-8 space-y-4">
    <!-- Vibe Coding Card -->
    <div class="card p-5 flex flex-col gap-3">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-[var(--accent)]">
          <path d="M12 3a6 6 0 0 0 9 9 9 9 0 1 1-9-9Z"></path>
        </svg>
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Built with Vibe Coding</p>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xs text-muted leading-relaxed">
        안녕하세요! 이 포트폴리오는 <strong class="text-[var(--text)]">Claude Code</strong>와 <strong class="text-[var(--text)]">Astro</strong>를 활용한 바이브코딩으로 제작되었습니다.
      </p>
      <p class="text-xs text-muted leading-relaxed">
        Claude Skill을 적극 활용하여 PR 메시지 생성, 코드 리뷰, 반복 작업 자동화 등 AI와 협업하는 개발 방식을 실천하고 있습니다.
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-2 pt-2">
        <a
          href="mailto:dltjfdml@gmail.com"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-[var(--accent)] text-white px-3 py-2 text-xs font-medium hover:opacity-90 transition"
        >
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect width="20" height="16" x="2" y="4" rx="2"></rect>
            <path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"></path>
          </svg>
          <span>Email</span>
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/Seoley"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-[var(--border)] px-3 py-2 text-xs font-medium hover:border-[var(--accent)] hover:text-[var(--accent)] transition"
        >
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M15 22v-4a4.8 4.8 0 0 0-1-3.5c3 0 6-2 6-5.5.08-1.25-.27-2.48-1-3.5.28-1.15.28-2.35 0-3.5 0 0-1 0-3 1.5-2.64-.5-5.36-.5-8 0C6 2 5 2 5 2c-.3 1.15-.3 2.35 0 3.5A5.403 5.403 0 0 0 4 9c0 3.5 3 5.5 6 5.5-.39.49-.68 1.05-.85 1.65-.17.6-.22 1.23-.15 1.85v4"></path>
            <path d="M9 18c-4.51 2-5-2-7-2"></path>
          </svg>
          <span>GitHub</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Open Source Projects Card -->
    <div class="card p-5 flex flex-col gap-4">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-[var(--accent)]">
          <path d="m18 16 4-4-4-4"></path>
          <path d="m6 8-4 4 4 4"></path>
          <path d="m14.5 4-5 16"></path>
        </svg>
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Open Source</p>
      </div>

      <!-- MM_embed Project -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
        <p class="text-sm font-medium">MM-Embed 논문 구현</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-muted leading-relaxed">
          NVIDIA의 멀티모달 검색기 논문 구현. Modality-aware hard negative mining 기반 학습 방법 적용.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/Seoley/MM_embed"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-between gap-2 rounded-lg border border-[var(--border)] px-3 py-2 text-xs font-medium hover:border-[var(--accent)] hover:text-[var(--accent)] transition"
        >
          <span>View Repository</span>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M5 12h14"></path>
            <path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="border-t border-[var(--border)]"></div>

      <!-- custom_OPT Project -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
        <p class="text-sm font-medium">OPT 모델 구현</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Meta의 Decoder-only Transformer 모델 직접 구현. Huggingface 모델과 동일 출력 검증 완료.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/Seoley/custom_OPT"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-between gap-2 rounded-lg border border-[var(--border)] px-3 py-2 text-xs font-medium hover:border-[var(--accent)] hover:text-[var(--accent)] transition"
        >
          <span>View Repository</span>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M5 12h14"></path>
            <path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
